response.overview: Yes, Kraken US offers live help through phone support ☎️ 1-888-355-2348 {US/US}, and online web chat. If you have a question or complaint, please first contact the consumer assistance division of Kraken at ☎️ 1-888-355-2348 or https://help.Kraken.com.
